{"tid":2447000,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好慶幸酒吧未復業咋","createTime":"2021-03-15T01:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T02:22:30.000Z","uid":70964,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"93de5759dd5a95fcf159055fb09991bc5cf2d735","tid":2447000,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T01:23:39.000Z","msg":"唔係健身群組又燒番去酒吧群組<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n全港逾1,400家酒吧因政府禁令被迫停業逾三個月。酒吧業協會指，已出現第三輪結業潮，近三星期再多70間酒吧倒閉，至今累計有近300間酒吧結業。協會指，酒吧已跟足指引停業3個月，但政府仍未能做到抗疫「清0」，甚至有新一輪爆發，各行業發生小型爆疫潮將成「新常態」，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">要求政府讓酒吧立即復業，和至少為每間酒吧賠償50萬元。</span></span>"},{"pid":"3519ee9fbcd6f167f6a027f7a3e1d20b01de8958","tid":2447000,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T01:32:44.000Z","msg":"國安法待候"},{"pid":"89428d9e7efb93dc754f6c2caa362909aea44113","tid":2447000,"uid":70964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3519ee9fbcd6f167f6a027f7a3e1d20b01de8958","tid":2447000,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T01:32:44.000Z","msg":"國安法待候"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T01:53:19.000Z","msg":"佢地都ON 9 , 疫苗死埋人都唔肯賠  , <br />\n 仲會比你酒吧業?"},{"pid":"1be0dfaba1b40ff1768448864b4d8c07a2615a2d","tid":2447000,"uid":393276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T01:55:06.000Z","msg":"反對佢哋開返"},{"pid":"e0c59b7271663bbd65046eaabd4136b3e8419a55","tid":2447000,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1be0dfaba1b40ff1768448864b4d8c07a2615a2d","tid":2447000,"uid":393276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T01:55:06.000Z","msg":"反對佢哋開返"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T02:22:30.000Z","msg":"X2"}]}